TCR phospho-signalling upon antibody-based stimulation

Marie Locard-Paulet

Tue Sep 04 17:19:34 2018

Results of enrichment analysis.

"KEAEnrichments" contains the results of phosphorylation site specific enrichment using KEA the 4th September 2018 (no background). I saved the enrichment results with the following labels: - KS for Literature Based Kinase-Substrate Library with Phosphosites, followed by the cluster number. - BT for Biological Terms Associated with Phosphosites from Literature Mining, followed by the cluster number. - AllReg is when I used all the regulated sites as input. - Background is when I used all the sites identified in the data set.

"PANTHER" contains the results of GO term enrichments based on the gene names using Panther the 4th September 2018. I used the detected sites as background.

"Phomics" contains the results of GO term enrichments based on the phosphorylation sites using Phomics the 4th September 2018. I used the detected sites as background.

The gene list used for the background is in the PANTHER folder.
